[6.130529, "o", "  \u001b[33m> coord_detect_conflicts session=alpha files=[src/auth.ts]\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[6.13155, "o", "## CONFLICTS DETECTED\r\n\r\n### Session Overlaps\r\n- **beta2222** (undefined): src/auth.ts вЂ” \"Write tests\"\r\n\r\n**Recommendation:** Coordinate before editing these files.\r\n\r\n"]
